<body> <h1 style="background-color:DodgerBlack;">INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY</h1>
<p>The Department of Information Technology deals with the dynamic analysis of an evolving plethora of information and applying it towards the manipulation of design and development of communication strategies.
<h2>Emphasis Here is given to:</h2>
<p>Quality education to comply with dynamic industry trends and global challenges.
<p>Acquainting the students with the latest technology in networking.
<p>To develop human resources with sound knowledge and intellectual capability for innovation, research and excellence in the field of Information Technology.
<p>This department has strong computer labs in the form of state-of-the-art IBM computers,with the latest softwares and internet facilities. Student computer ratio is 1:1.
